中国战机进入台湾防空识别区
台湾派出飞机，广播无线电警告，部署防空导弹
By Eric Chang, Taiwan News, 2022/03/07 10:21 MND photo
TAIPEI - A Chinese fighter jet entered Taiwan’s air defense identification zone (ADIZ) on Sunday (March 6), marking the second intrusion this month.
周日（3月6日）一架中国战斗机进入台湾防空识别区标志着本月第二次入侵
据国防部（MND）称，一架中国人民解放军空军（PLAAF）沈阳歼16战斗机飞入防空识别区西南角。 台湾派出飞机，发布无线电警告，并部署防空导弹系统对其进行跟踪
A single People’s Liberation Army Air Force (PLAAF) Shenyang J-16 fighter plane flew into the southwest corner of the ADIZ, according to the Ministry of National Defense (MND). Taiwan sent aircraft, issued radio warnings, and deployed air defense missile systems to track it.
